袭击事件与受害者宗教信仰和当前巴以冲突有关系。这引发美国各界对仇恨犯罪的担忧。 比利时首都布鲁塞尔 16 日晚发生枪击事件，造成两名瑞典球迷死亡，另有一人受伤。比利时国家危机中心随后宣布，布鲁塞尔大区的安全警戒级别提升至最高级 4 级。一名自称凶手的人在社交媒体上宣称，自己效忠极端组织「伊斯兰国」。 18 日至 19 日，美国在中东地区多个军事基地连续遭袭。美军中央司令部已证实，美军在伊拉克的基地遭袭并造成军人受伤。突发！多国爆发致命袭击，美军多个基地遭袭！"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-16245a3c1c61eafa09223e9c83a550f8_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "59 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/626983350"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIp9+Y87q5y5N0EAMaCTEwMTYwODYyMSCagcipBjAAOLEEQBNyCTYyNjk4MzM1MHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "20_1697796247.928054", "card_id": "Q_48475096", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 316}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "武汉有哪些值得一去的餐馆，馆子里一定要尝试的菜式有哪些？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "这里说的馆子包括小吃和正餐，不论中高低，好吃的还请都多推荐，感激不尽！"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "59 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/48475096"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4Ip9+Y87q5y5N0EAMaCDExNjA1MzgyILmCnLwFMAA4ijJAFHIINDg0NzUwOTZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "21_1697796247.928738", "card_id": "Q_626917543", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 373}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "10 月 20 日天猫双 11 发布会提出了 85 折新玩法，有哪些值得关注的信息？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "听说了嘛！今年天猫双 11 又出新玩法了，爱好薅羊毛的天猫不允许大家错过这条消息，本互联网攻略替，想问问大家今年的双 11 上有哪些值得关注的信息？"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "56 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/626917543"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIp9+Y87q5y5N0EAMaCTE